{
  "stem": "26140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, one night, came a German official who said my parents didn't live in Poznan any longer, they were from eastern Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they asked us to be evacuated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said to my father that my mother can stay with the children, but the father must move.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother said, no, we go together with our father, because I cannot support the family on my own.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we moved to where they moved us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That means they moved us first to Chenstochov, where we stayed at a-- well, it was a church community, where they gave us food and supplied us with living accommodation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's-- that's about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later on, I've tried to move to Hungary with my brother--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no encounter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had encounter with some soldiers when I was trying to get some milk, which was shortage of.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't know allow big queues.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- one day, they kicked me and said, you go away from there, and don't stand anymore in the queues to get the food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they kicked me on the bottom once, and that's about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I moved right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see much there, because I didn't stay long after the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we tried to-- my two older brothers moved to south Poland in order to go through the Hungarian border, in order to join the Polish forces.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, we received a letter that they passed the border, and they were happy to be in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I, with my twin brother and older brother Zygmunt, tried to move as well to south Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we weren't very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were caught on the border, on the Hungarian border, near the town Bukowsko.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after interrogations--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
